{"tid":497021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實聰明人都幾慘","createTime":"2017-12-12T10:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T08:52:01.000Z","uid":99048,"like":31,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f7013b7c1cdf1695b72926ba20718cccf605eaa8","tid":497021,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"日日睇住蠢人做傻事<br />\n<br />\n佢地隨波逐流，做牆頭草，做事說話冇準則<br />\n<br />\n俾商人政府玩同利用，有太多太多事<br />\n<br />\n偏偏蠢人佔大多數<br />\n<br />\n講出真相/某些價值觀係錯，佢地又唔信<br />\n<br />\n仲要成日好開心咁<br />\n<br />\n聰明個班知道改變唔到咩<br />\n<br />\n焗住要扮傻扮唔知，迎合主流<br />\n<br />\n睇住個屋企人／朋友／社會繼續做傻事<br />\n<br />\n都唔知係自己傻定呢個社會傻<br />\n<br />\n呢種感覺唔好受<br />\n<br />\n覺得咩都唔知反而冇咁悲觀<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7472d06bb9b3dea17d27e2d5580a6f159004a16f","tid":497021,"uid":50328,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3b7adc403486417668dc2b4a1c140f76d1fee08","tid":497021,"uid":78781,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"改變唔到d咩仲可以稱為聰明人？"},{"pid":"f37c579544fb0eb9137131edcc95ac2860b029eb","tid":497021,"uid":76756,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"命運就像是輪姦,反抗不亞,不如試著去享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a41cdbf3d04e24880a9ffd9c092dc3b7195b8ab","tid":497021,"uid":76756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>命運就像是輪姦,反抗不了,不如試著去享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5bf3e2e0653160738f471f784217119dc00d180b","tid":497021,"uid":60959,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"最撚慘係果啲以為自己聰明但實質蠢閪嘅人，即係樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13455edc16f12f310ece28dd